      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HIGH FIVE INDI (1) turned in a better effort at The Meadows last start, finishing third behind Fromelles Poppy (30.82) in a Mix 6/7. Turned chasing the leaders but kept coming. Strong form has emerged from her last run. Expected to feature in the finish again. RAE'S RAINBOW (4) made light work of a wide draw last time with a strong early sectional and clocking 24.42 in a 0.8 lengths win at this track over 425m. The form out of her last race has been franked. One of the leading chances again. GRAY GROUPER (8) had a tough draw to overcome and was game in defeat when only a neck from Beast Ablaze in second (24.33) at this track. Leading chance. LIGHTHEARTEDNESS (3) surprised many when in the placings last start - deserves some thought.",
